title: XTOOL AD20PRO OBD2 Scanner All System Trouble Code Reader Oil Reset Battery Test
item_description:
2024 Advanced XTOOL AD20 Pro Code Reader >>>Best Doctor for Your Beloved Car
An Upgraded Version of AD10/AD20 BT OBD2 Scanner, AD20 Pro provides you with better performance.
👍All System Diagnostics: AD20pro features Full system diagnosis function to read and clear fault codes, e.g Engines, Auto Transmission, ABS, SRS, etc. all available systems of your car.
👍 Full OBD2 tests: Include Read and Clear DTCs, Freeze Frame, O2 Sensor Test, On-Board Monitor Test, I/M Readiness status, Live Data Stream in text, component Test, Vehicle Information, etc. Advancer App will remind you once a fault code arises.
👍 Check Engine Light On: When your car detects an emissi0n-related problem, the Check Engine Light will be turned on. With XTOOL AD20 Pro car reader, you can read code to quickly find out why the check engine light is on and turn it off, which greatly saves the cost of expensive repairs.
👍 Maintenance Light Reset（Oil Light Reset）: Help reset automotive change oil and maintenance required lights.(One of the functions more than AD20)
👍 BT 5.0 Connectivity: Enabling faster and more stable communication with mobile devices. It allows for efficient reading and clearing of vehicle fault codes, surpassing the capabilities of BT 3.0 versions.
👍 DTC Definition: AD20 Pro Automotive code reader can look up the complicated fault code's definition directly, including the fault description, possible causes of the fault, maintenance suggestion and background knowledge, no need to search online. (Note: DTC lookup is only available for generic OBDII fault codes, not available for other system fault codes at the moment.)
👍 Performance Test: Test your vehicle by the terms of acceleration time for 100 kilometers, Top speed, Engine Load, Coolant Temperature to see how the vehicle performs so that you can detect potential problems with its powertrain, brakes, or other systems.
👍 Wide Compatibility: Work on most of 1996 and later American, European, Asian 12v cars. XTOOL AD20 Pro Mini OBDII adapter supports all OBD2 Protocols including the newer CAN protocol.
👍 Convenient, Light, Portable: XTOOL AD20 Pro auto diagnostic scanner is designed to be user-friendly, light and small, no cable needed and easy to carry. You can scan your car anytime and anywhere taking it out of your pocket or just leave it plugged in.
👍 Multilingual:  9 common languages available, including English, Spanish, Russian, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Korean,Arabic (Change the language directly in the APP) .
Note: Does not work with other APP., AD20 PRO APP supports 64-bit Android devices but cannot support 32-bit Android devices.

XTOOL AD20 Pro OBD2 Scanner Diagnostic Tool >>> Supports Full Systems Diagnosis
XTOOL AD20 Pro can access all available ECUs of car to read and clear codes for a wide range of car models, making it a must-have automotive diagnostic tool.
Include : ABS System, Engine System, SAS System, TPMS System, IMMO System, Battery System, SRS System, Air Conditioning System, Transmission System, etc...
Note: It doesn't offer live data provided for all system fault codes currently.
What Can the XTOOL AD20 Pro Enhanced OBD2 Code Reader Do? >>> 10 Modes of OBD2 Tests
✅ Read Codes & Clear Codes: Quickly read and clear check engine light codes including generic, manufacturer-specific, and pending codes, helping you save time and money to fix it yourself if possible.
✅ Live Data Stream: Live data stream can show some vital vehicle data in text to monitor your vehicle status such as engine load, RPM, fuel trims, coolant temperature, misfire counters. Note: Live data graphing is not available.
✅ Freeze Frame: Records the certain vehicle conditions when an emissi0n-related fault occurs.
✅ I/M Readiness Stauts: Determine if your vehicle is ready for quick state e-missions readiness check and drive cycle verification.
✅ O2 Sensor Test: Allows retrieval and viewing of O2 sensor monitor test results for the most recently performed test from the vehicle’s on-board computer.
✅ On-Board Monitor Test(Mode 6): Advanced test results (like misfire counts) for On-Board Diagnostic System Monitors.
✅ View Vehicle Information: Display the information such as VIN (Vehicle Identification Number), CID (Calibration ID) and CVN (Calibration verification number), etc.
✅ Component Test(Mode 08): Plug it into the vehicle's computer and determines that the emissi0n system and components are working properly.
✅ DTC Lookup Library: AD20 Pro code reader offers the OBD2 fault code's definition directly, including the fault description, the cause of the fault, maintenance suggestions and background knowledge, saves your searching time online and help you better understand the fault co*de definition.
XTOOL AD20 Pro Car Diagnostic Tool >>> Capable of Maintenance Light Reset Function
Every time your car is maintained, you can use this AD20 Pro to reset the maintenance light of your car, so as to be more prepared to record the time of the next maintenance
How to Quick Start this OBD2 Code Reader?
♦️ Download App: Advancer AD20 Pro
- For iOS: Get it on App Store
- For Android: Get it on Google Play
If AD20 Pro APP user registration prompts email error or server error, it may be that the email address is not supported, change the email address and try again.
♦️ Activate the device
♦️ Plug in your Vehicles
♦️ BT Pairing
♦️ Start Engine
- Note: Make sure your mobile devices are not paried with other devices.
♦️ Open the "Advancer AD20 Pro" APP and start a quick test.
